 dialoger, dans, film, lys, musikk, sang. Det burde v\u00e6re un\u00f8dvendig \u00e5 p\u00e5 toppen av dette bli fortalt hva som skjer av en forteller.", "Men likevel alts\u00e5, en mektig opplevelse, formidlet av toppakt\u00f8rer i en rekke kunstneriske sjangre.", "Anmeldt av OLE JACOB HOEL"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "6efa5885a8541e2ea7e84ec209cca154ab7c0319cc25764567d297cb1fad4f33"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-06T11:44:14.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "I sitt andre \u00e5r er familieforestillingen om Olav den hellige i Nidarosdomen blitt en mer helhetlig forestilling."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/article10224724.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/omw_Olav-Domen.07.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/f1e2ccd95a47a18bf6c48eda58834519bb44ebc1.jpg?596de54b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Mektig forbedring -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "f1e2ccd95a47a18bf6c48eda58834519bb44ebc1"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "kultur"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["mektig", "mektig forbedring", "forestilling"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["nidarosdomen", "olav", "olavsfestdagene"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "norge"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["erik hivju", "rolf hoff balzersens", "stian hovland pedersen", "kristoffer hivju", "hildegunn eggen"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["pluss"